; Regression test for issue #512: --lots does not work with commodities conversion
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/512
; The C (commodity conversion) directive should cause BTC to be displayed as bits,
; but --lots shows 1.5 BTC instead of converting to 1,500,000.00 bit.

D 1,000.00 USD

C BTC 1 = 1,000,000.00 bit

2018-01-23 Buy BTC
    Crypto:BTC                             500000.00 bit @@ 5000 USD
    Exchange

2018-01-23 Buy BTC
    Crypto:BTC                             1.5 BTC @@ 15000 USD
    Exchange

test bal --lots
             1.5 BTC
500,000.00 bit {0.01 USD} [2018/01/23]  Crypto:BTC
      -20,000.00 USD  Exchange
--------------------
             1.5 BTC
      -20,000.00 USD
500,000.00 bit {0.01 USD} [2018/01/23]
end test
